high_descs: To right and face the black kitchen table.
Pick the potato up from off of the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk to black shelf next to the counter.
Place the potato on to the black shelf.
Turn around, go to the left, and face the counter top next to the stove.
Pick the yellow knife up from off of the counter.
Go to the left and stand in front of the black shelf.
Cut the potato that is on the black shelf.
Turn around and walk across the room to stand in front of the coffee maker.
Cut the potato in the green bucket under the coffee maker in to slices.
Place the knife in to the green bucket.
Pick up one of the slices of potato.
Turn around and walk towards the black shelf at the end of the counter.
Place the potato slice on to the black shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a sliced piece of potato on top of the black shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the coffee maker, turn right to face the round black table.
Take the potato next to the fork from the table.
Turn right, go straight and to the left to the black stand next to the white table.
Put the potato on the lower right corner of the stand.
Turn right, go to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn around, go to the door, turn right, go to the black stand.
Cut the potato on the stand into slices.
Turn around, go to the counter with the coffee maker.
Cut the potato in the green bin into slices below the coffee maker counter.
Put the knife in the green bin.
Take a slice of potato from the green bin.
Turn around, go back to the black stand.
Put the slice of potato to the left of the sliced potato on the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of potato next to another sliced potato on a stand.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right twice, walk towards the table
Grab the potato from the round table
Walk with the potato towards the small corner table
Set the potato on the corner table
Walk towards the counter next to the stove
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk with the knife towards the small corner table
Slice the potato on the table
Walk with the knife towards the round table
slice the potato on the plastic pot under the counter
Move the apple next to it
Pick up a slice of the potato
Walk with the slice of potato towards the small corner table
Set the slice of potato on the corner table
anns.task_desc: Slice both potatoes, bring a slice from the under the counter pot set it on the table
